OL,3,C'Catastrophic' prison overcrowding:
OL,4,CEmergency plans to be announced
OL,6,FEmergency measures to deal with
OL,7,F"catastrophic" prison overcrowding
OL,8,Fwill be set out by the Justice
OL,9,FSecretary on Friday - amid fears
OL,10,Fprisons could run out of space within
OL,11,Fweeks.
OL,13,FShabana Mahmood is expected to argue
OL,14,Fthe level of overcrowding, described
OL,15,Fby the Ministry of Justice as
OL,16,F"catastrophic", requires "immediate
OL,17,Faction" to "pull the justice system
OL,18,Fback from the brink of total collapse".
