OL,3,C'Catastrophic' prison overcrowding:
OL,4,CEmergency plans to be announced
OL,6,FFollowing a tour of HMP Bedford and
OL,7,FHMP Five Wells, in Northamptonshire,
OL,8,FMahmood will set out plans that could
OL,9,Finclude reducing the time before some
OL,10,Fprisoners are automatically released.
OL,12,FThe emergency measures are being
OL,13,Fannounced in a bid to prevent the
OL,14,Fsituation from becoming so bad that it
OL,15,Fleads to a breakdown in law and order,
OL,16,Famid fears that if no action is taken
OL,17,Fthis could see a scenario where police
OL,18,Fofficers cannot use their powers to
OL,19,Fdetain dangerous offenders because
OL,20,Fthey have nowhere to hold them.
