OL,3,C'Catastrophic' prison overcrowding:
OL,4,CEmergency plans to be announced
OL,6,F"We're operationally in trouble at
OL,7,Fless than 300 spaces left," they said.
OL,9,FOn Thursday, the Prime Minister said
OL,10,Fthe scale of the problem was "worse
OL,11,Fthan I thought" and expressed anger at
OL,12,Fbeing faced with taking emergency
OL,13,Fmeasures so early in his premiership.
OL,15,FOne of the moves expected to be
OL,16,Fannounced is a reduction in the amount
OL,17,Fof a sentence a prisoner must serve
OL,18,Fbefore being automatically released.
