OL,3,C'Catastrophic' prison overcrowding:
OL,4,CEmergency plans to be announced
OL,6,FMost prisoners currently serve 50% of
OL,7,Ftheir sentence in jail, with the
OL,8,Fremaining 50% being served on licence
OL,9,Fand under threat of being returned to
OL,10,Fprison if they break their parole
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,FBut Friday's announcement could see
OL,14,Fthat reduced to 40%, a move the former
OL,15,FConservative justice secretary Alex
OL,16,FChalk reportedly pressed Rishi Sunak
OL,17,Fto make before the election.
