OL,3,C'Catastrophic' prison overcrowding:
OL,4,CEmergency plans to be announced
OL,6,F"We're very vulnerable to shocks in
OL,7,Fthe estate. That can be big, high
OL,8,Fprofile shocks, like the 2011 civil
OL,9,Fdisorder, like a prison riot or it
OL,10,Fcould actually be much more mundane
OL,11,Fthings like an outbreak of bedbugs
OL,12,Fthat would require us to close the
OL,13,Fwing, and fumigate it for two or three
OL,14,Fweeks. We are very vulnerable to
OL,15,Fshocks at this level," they continued.
OL,17,FThe source also stressed that
OL,18,Fprobation officers need sufficient
OL,19,Ftime to plan for an offender's release
OL,20,Fto make sure victims are protected.
