OL,3,C'Catastrophic' prison overcrowding:
OL,4,CEmergency plans to be announced
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice is already
OL,7,Fbuilding six new prisons to create an
OL,8,Fextra 20,000 places as demand grows
OL,9,Ffor cell spaces, partially because of
OL,10,Fthe Government's campaign to hire
OL,11,F20,000 more police officers.
OL,13,FAbout 6,000 spaces have been created
OL,14,Falready and about 10,000 will be built
OL,15,Fby the end of 2025.
OL,17,FOn Thursday, campaigners urged Starmer
OL,18,Fto look at reforming Imprisonment for
OL,19,FPublic Protection sentences as a way
OL,20,Fto ease overcrowding.
