OL,4,CEmergency plans to be announced
OL,6,FThe IPP scandal, which was brought in
OL,7,Fby the last Labour government and then
OL,8,Fabolished over a decade ago, has seen
OL,9,Fthousands of prisoners behind bars
OL,10,Findefinitely.
OL,12,FCampaigners argue that resentencing or
OL,13,Freleasing IPP prisoners could help
OL,14,Fwith the pressing issue of
OL,15,Foverpopulated prisons.
